message.body: Feel free to come to Picasso tonight to hear the band

I am in bed already like the people from Saida. (The stupid town where I grew up). They are in their pjs by 4pm! I am sleepy from too much clo... whatever. I have been trying to learn the name of this drug for two weeks now. Enjoy the evening. I want to get out more, but not tonight...thanks for thinking of me.
